headline: Prediction: AMD Could Surge by 111% in the Next 2 Years
summary: AMD just delivered its fastest revenue growth since 2022.  The company is benefiting from adoption of its AI accelerators and market share gains in the PC market.  Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD) has been one of the biggest success stories over the last decade in the semiconductor industry.
